{"tid":400411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人留一個叫得郁我老豆睇醫生嘅方法。","createTime":"2017-09-14T18:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T22:48:47.000Z","uid":137255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3ae7ef7a2a402ab7a7f59461a035cf2468a511","tid":400411,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:29:10.000Z","msg":"我老豆10年前曾經爆過血管，宜家係做冷氣維修嘅。<br />\n平時朝9晚8都係得佢一條友同一兩個伙記做。<br />\n呢一兩年，佢真係好辛苦，尤其係夏天，佢基本上冇得休息咁濟，30度都喺户外暴曬。<br />\n宜家佢由上個月開始就係咁咳，一直話冇嘢冇嘢，又唔肯去睇醫生，我真係唔知點解佢咁硬頸...<br />\n我好驚佢唔係咩傷風感冒，而係身體有咩事...<br />\n我應該點叫佢去睇醫生...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95a412613fc3ed404768b5467bf47902f9becbd","tid":400411,"uid":138740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:32:48.000Z","msg":"扮係你要睇 叫佢陪你"},{"pid":"7a89917a8c0960c560059b58a90fd9f3715b6aee","tid":400411,"uid":1531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:35:16.000Z","msg":"比份棺材報價表佢<br />\n<br />\n叫佢二揀一"},{"pid":"ca7ecb973ea3cafcddb1b472d7e1ac8c521ac412","tid":400411,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮係你要睇 叫佢陪你</blockquote><br />\n我廿幾歲叫佢陪我睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢唔會信掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f700a17aa725ccb3e744c3aeb1e78cf553e3d2","tid":400411,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:40:35.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"16ee0c2755b3611359cfb9d35f8b7e5dd4a8b9c1","tid":400411,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T18:40:48.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"f1aeddbc8